[02:06] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'It uses a combination of two techniques. The first one is called latent panel anchoring, and the second one is reciprocal attention value mixing. So this first one basically helps keep the'

[02:18] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'characters consistent across images using a shared reference image. And then for the second component, this basically blends the features of the reference image with the generated images to'

[02:30] [scene:talk]
